metadata.name: The Tomb Keeper
metadata.description: This is The Genesis Artwork For Project "OUMM". All Artwork Has a Storyline and Significance in The grand story of OUMM. OUMM is a world filled with adventures and Mysteries. This is a Beautiful, Rare, and elusive Peacock betta fish Only Heard of in myths.OUMM is a Completely Unique World, CReated BY Kreator Kaus. The project aims to Tell a Story of adventure, Myth, Mystics, and Politics. It aims to build a community and turn it into a Working sustainable metaverse with endless adventures and unique storyline and artwork. The Groundwork for OUMM has already been initiated and the initial artwork will be available as an NFT collection. Bridging the gap between reality and dreams.
